@startuml
title POI查询时序图

skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor black
    ArrowFontColor black
    ActorBorderColor black
    ActorBackgroundColor white
    ActorFontColor black
    ParticipantBorderColor black
    ParticipantBackgroundColor white
    ParticipantFontColor black
    LifeLineBorderColor black
    LifeLineBackgroundColor white
    DividerBorderColor none
    DividerBackgroundColor transparent
    DividerFontColor black
    DividerFontStyle normal  ' 取消加粗，普通字体
}

actor "用户" as User
participant "前端" as Frontend
participant "后端" as Backend
participant "Redis" as Redis
participant "高德地图API" as Gaode
participant "DeepSeekAPI" as AI

User -> Frontend : 选点获得浏览语音
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Backend : GET /api/getPoi (经纬度, 用户ID)
activate Backend

Backend -> Redis : 检查缓存
activate Redis
Redis --> Backend : 返回缓存结果
deactivate Redis

Backend -> Gaode : 请求逆地理编码
activate Gaode
Gaode --> Backend : 返回POI信息
deactivate Gaode

Backend -> AI : 生成POI浏览内容
activate AI
AI --> Backend : 返回浏览文本
deactivate AI

Backend -> Redis : 缓存浏览摘要
activate Redis
Redis --> Backend : 确认缓存
deactivate Redis

Backend --> Frontend : 返回浏览文本
deactivate Backend

Frontend -> Frontend : 播放浏览语音
Frontend --> User : 收听浏览语音
deactivate Frontend

@enduml